A man is due to appear at the Mmabatho Magistrates&#8217; Court on Monday for illegal possession of firearm and ammunition as well as possession of dagga.The 50-year-old man was arrested on Friday at Tloung village in Mahikeng after police responded quickly to a tip-off that the man was dealing in dagga.Police conducted a search leading to discovery of a box containing 50 ammunition and a pistol loaded with 7 rounds of ammunition. They also found dagga contained in two plastics.The suspect was then apprehended for dealing in dagga and illegal possession of firearm and ammunition.-TNA Reporter 